<div class="container">
  <div class="page-header text-center">
    <h1>代購接受！</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-6">
    <%= image_tag @order.line_item.product.picture.url, class: 'center-block' %>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-6">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
        <table class="table acceptance">
          <tr>
            <th>產品名稱</th>
            <td><%= @order.line_item.product.name %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>單價</th>
            <td><%= number_to_currency(@order.line_item.product.price * 0.28, precision: 0) %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>數量</th>
            <td><%= @order.line_item.quantity %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>BeMine 將支付您</th>
            <td><%= number_to_currency(@order.line_item.product.price * 0.28, precision: 0) %></td>
          </tr>
        </table>
        <p>請將於5天內把產品寄至 BeMine 收購中心</p>
        <address>104台北市中山區南京東路二段97號、號5樓</address>
        <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3614.4629278888415!2d121.53007031476685!3d25.05229424371227!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3442a96126c50265%3A0xf47e458e3751f344!2zMTA05Y-w5YyX5biC5Lit5bGx5Y2A5Y2X5Lqs5p2x6Lev5LqM5q61OTfomZ8!5e0!3m2!1szh-TW!2stw!4v1453995057649" width="100%" height="400" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>